Package kaitech.controller

Class SuppliersController

  • java.lang.Object
    • kaitech.controller.SuppliersController
  • public class SuppliersController
extends java.lang.Object
    The controller for the supplier screen, which is a list of all the suppliers. Can add/delete/modify suppliers provided the user is logged in.
